panded its production from the original milling capacity of 30 to 60 metric ton of FFB per hour. YLPOI is committed to produce quality products which meet customers\' satisfaction.</p>\r\n','<p>Since 1988 in its efforts to strive for milling competency, YLPOI has annually been participating in the milling competency award conducted by the Malaysian Palm Oil Board (MPOB). It has been awarded the Milling Certificate of Competency since 1988.</p>\r\n','','','','','','','',0,'<h4 class=\"title\">CONTACT</h4>\r\n','','<ul class=\"contact-info\"><li><i class=\"icon-map-marker\"></i> <strong>Address:</strong> Lot 9399 Bidor Industrial Estate, 35500 Bidor, Perak Darul Ridzuan, Malaysia.</li><li class=\"line\"><br/></li><li><i class=\"icon-phone\"></i> <strong>Phone:</strong> +(605) 434 1481 / 434 1669</li><li class=\"line\"><br/></li><li><i class=\"icon-print\"></i> <strong>Fax:</strong> +(605) 434 3910</li><li class=\"line\"><br/></li><li><i class=\"icon-envelope\"></i> <strong>Email:</strong> <a href=\"mailto:kclee@ylpo.com.my\" data-cke-saved-href=\"mailto:kclee@ylpo.com.my\">kclee@ylpo.com.my</a></li><li class=\"line\"><br/></li><li><i class=\"icon-envelope\"></i> <strong>Email:</strong> <a href=\"mailto:shashi@ylpo.com.my\" data-cke-saved-href=\"mailto:shashi@ylpo.com.my\">shashi@ylpo.com.my</a></li><li class=\"line\"><br/></li></ul>\r\n<footer class=\"project-footer\"> <a class=\"button\" href=\"#\"><span class=\"button-inner\"><i class=\"icon-double-angle-right\"></i> Visit Site</span> </a> </footer>','<h3>PROCESSES</h3>\r\n','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','2015-02-12 02:33:47','2015-02-12 02:33:47'),(649,'hospitality',1,'<h1>Hospitality</h1>\r\n','<h3 class=\"entry-title\">HOSPITALITY DIVISION</h3>\r\n','<h3 class=\"title\">Sabah Tea Resort Sdn Bhd (1001721-V)</h3>\r\n','<figure class=\"thumb alignleft\"><img alt=\"Sabah Tea Resort\" src=\"/~yeelee72185perak/laravel/public/images/logo/img_sabah_tea_resort.jpg\" /></figure>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Sabah Tea Resort Sdn Bhd</strong> (STR) is involved in tourism activities. Its Sabah Tea Garden is situated within the single largest tea plantation in Borneo in the highlands of Mount Kinabalu. It offers a unique tourist destination for those interested in Borneo\'s well-known rainforest and cultural diversity.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Facilities available include: -</p>\r\n','<ul>\r\n	<li>Accommodation in the form of longhouses, cottages or guest house as well as camping grounds.</li>\r\n	<li>Restaurant specializing in both chinese and western cuisine.</li>\r\n	<li>Local cultural performances.</li>\r\n	<li>In-house guides for jungle walks.</li>\r\n	<li>Trails for jungle trekking, mountain biking and a multitude of outdoor activities.</li>\r\n	<li>Tour of tea manufacturing facility.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n','','','<h4 class=\"title\">Contact</h4>\r\n','','','<ul class=\"contact-info\"><li><i class=\"icon-map-marker\"></i> <strong>Address:</strong> Km 18, Jalan Ranau-Sandakan, Kg Nalapak, 89309 Ranau, Sabah, Malaysia.</li><li class=\"line\"><br/></li><li><i class=\"icon-phone\"></i> <strong>Phone:</strong> +(6088) 440 882 (KK Office) / +(6088) 876 611 (Ranau-Reception Counter)</li><li class=\"line\"><br/></li><li><i class=\"icon-print\"></i> <strong>Fax:</strong> +(6088) 440 886</li><li class=\"line\"><br/></li><li><i class=\"icon-envelope\"></i> <strong>Email:</strong> <a href=\"mailto:info@sabahtea.net\" data-cke-saved-href=\"mailto:info@sabahtea.net\">info@sabahtea.net</a></li><li class=\"line\"><br/></li><li><i class=\"icon-globe\"></i> <strong>Website:</strong> <a href=\"http://www.sabahtea.com.my\" data-cke-saved-href=\"http://www.sabahtea.com.my\" target=\"_blank\">www.sabahtea.com.my</a></li><li class=\"line\"><br/></li></ul>','<footer class=\"project-footer\"> <a class=\"button\" href=\"http://www.sabahtea.com.my\"><span class=\"button-inner\"><i class=\"icon-double-angle-right\"></i> Visit Site</span> </a> </footer>','